&lt;li&gt;Ability to follow technical procedures and maintain accurate records&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and reliability&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
